                        <foreign>Reg. Petr. Diac.</foreign> fol. 152r, n. 349; <foreign>Registrum
                        Petri Diaconi (Montecassino, Archivio dell’abbazia, Reg.3)</foreign>,
                    Istituto Storico Italiano per il Medioevo e École Française de Rome, 2016, vol.
                    II, p. 1012 (source of the text reproduced here).</p>
            </div>
